original: Bondeman, Olof (Olle) Fredrik Johan Valdemar, tandläkare, Jönköping, f. 16/8/07 i Nävelsjö, Jönköp. 1. G. 35 m. Anna Björk. Barn: Anders f. 37, Kristina 39. — Studiex. v. Jönköp. h. a. 1. 27, Cand. med. dent. i Berlin 29, tandläk. i Sthlm 32. Prakt, i Jönköp. sed. 32.
translated: Bondeman, Olof (Olle) Fredrik Johan Valdemar, dentist, Jönköping, b. August 16th, 1907 in Nävelsjö, Jönköping. Married once, in 1935 to Anna Björk. Children: Anders b. 1937, Kristina b. 1939. He studied at Jönköping university beginning in 1927 and earned his degree in dentistry from Berlin University in 1929. He worked as a dentist in Stockholm from 1932 and began his own practice in Jönköping in 1932.
